Our mission

Sustainable future for the hospitality industry and the world trends are shifting to the wild nature locations around the globe to choose the most unique spot in the middle of nowhere.

"We are seeing our mission to be the part of the global changes and follow the international world class hospaitality standards and safety"

Saleh Mohsen Ali Alsowaidi

Project Manager, Assistant to the CEO

Vision

We choose 5 elements of the nature around us to build an eco resort on the highest world-class standards, creating a sustainable haven of tranquility and luxury.

The United Arab Emirates is the perfect and unique natures, which united all the most beautiful reserve spots in the world.

There are the most beautiful beaches, fantastic great mountains and Hatta lake, Mangroves plants and of course an amazing desert surrounding the cities.

Current project

The first in the region - Sand Elements Wellness Retreat to be started from the beautiful Dubai desert and natural reserve Al Qudra Lakes.
